{"tid":586064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【這就是強國】愛情表白標語被指暗諷習近平 傳言會追究掛布條者的責任","createTime":"2018-03-09T08:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T08:40:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"267ef7ca9261126c609ff1e0b1bb27308f711f85","tid":586064,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180308/640_f7e394677e69ccc44766300e3834a3af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180308%2F640_f7e394677e69ccc44766300e3834a3af.jpg&h=11e3de73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">翻攝推特</span><br />\n<br />\n大學生浪漫表白說「愛你沒有期限」，竟然觸動中國高層的敏感神經！一幅寫著「愛你沒有期限」等字眼的標語，竟然掛出來沒多久就遭撤下，甚至還有傳言指，校方會追究掛布條者的責任，顯然「沒有期限」被認定在暗諷中國國家主席習近平修憲，踩到紅線。<br />\n<br />\n中國大學生在3月7日度過「女生節」，北京清華大學校園掛著許多向女生告白的布條，但其中一條寫的是「愛你沒有期限，如果有，那就把它刪掉」，這布條掛出不到半天，即遭人撤下，有傳言指校方要追究院系負責人的責任，但並未獲得證實，中國微博上的相關照片、貼文，據稱也都被刪光光。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在推特上宣稱，今年清大法學院同學經過投票篩選出女生節要掛的標語，但每一句候選標語不是緊扣修憲就是跟小熊維尼有關，例如「一往情深，十年不足為限」、「愛你，沒有期限」、「愛你沒有期限，如果有，那就把它刪掉」、「我還是喜歡你，像小熊喜歡糖衣」、「找到一個自己喜歡的東西，然後永不放手」「 愛你就為你修仙（諧音修憲），健康工作五十年。」<br />\n<br />\n對於學生標語遭到撤下的傳言，中國網友也戲謔說：「他這麼敏感，他爸爸知道嗎？」（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180308/640_e8c96e7da4441346b1b60a098c1a6ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180308%2F640_e8c96e7da4441346b1b60a098c1a6ef7.jpg&h=9022b45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180308/1311039/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180308%2F1311039%2F&d=bIjzDQ3e2DTBqJS7sv%2B8yzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=53d21367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180308%2F1311039%2F&h=be4817f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180308/1311039/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾中共捉到嘅話刑期都係沒有期限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac5b2355f92cb8f89cab09af88e22b3e159f3c7","tid":586064,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"btw點解強國堆banner咁鍾意用紅底白字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前amazon單新聞都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43eeaf54e8834fef882534f46913276594385a78","tid":586064,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"唔錯唔錯"},{"pid":"27eddbef048e7fb240a4c8cf5bde80f2ede64281","tid":586064,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"崩口人忌崩口碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b02ef80ce8bcaa4f15d59db9f79c91078940d9","tid":586064,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac5b2355f92cb8f89cab09af88e22b3e159f3c7","tid":586064,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"btw點解強國堆banner咁鍾意用紅底白字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前amazon單新聞都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.reactiongifs.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/bad-food.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reactiongifs.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F11%2Fbad-food.gif&h=0f642f84&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}